imba Mata) VASHISTH HOT SPRINGS (Dedicated to Vashisth Muni &amp; Renowned for its hot Curable water),CLUB HOUSE. Later free to explore the local market (MALL ROAD &amp; IBEX MARKET) of Manali, TIBETAN MONASTERY AND VAN VIHAR by own. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.\";i:5;s:377:\"MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only\r\nToday have excursion trip to ROHTANG PASS up to snow line (up to Snow line refers to the barrier placed by the government to avoid risks during Heavy snowfall).  Tour to Rohtang covers some of the most attractive spots, panorama activities and spectacular sight of glaciers. IN EVENING RETURN TO MANALI. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.\";i:6;s:181:\"MEALS:  Breakfast &amp; Dinner\r\nToday morning after breakfast checkout from the hotel and drive to Chandigarh. Reach Chandigarh and check in to the hotel. Dinner and overnight stay.\";i:7;s:238:\"MEALS:  Breakfast only\r\nToday have breakfast and check out from the hotel. Visit Rose Garden, Rock Garden &amp; Sukhna Lake and drive to Delhi. Reach Delhi and you will dropped at Delhi railway station or airport for your further journey.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:7:{i:1;s:210:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On arrival Delhi Airport you will meet with our assisted and drive for Shimla, on arrival check in to the hotel, Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel…&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:340:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today morning after breakfast proceed towards famous ski Point - KUFRI (Including Kufri Fun Park).  Rest of the evening free to explore THE MALL ROAD, RIDGE, SCANDAL POINT, LAKKAR BAZAAR, CHRIST CHURCH AND LOWER BAZAAR BY OWN. Dinner &amp; Overnight stay at the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:342:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS:  Breakfast &amp; Dinner&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out from the hotel and drive to Shimla enrooted visit Kullu, valley, Kullu shawl industry, Vaishno Devi Temple. Have photographs at Pandoh Dam &amp; Sundernaggar Lake. Ev