er and overnight stay at hotel.\";i:5;s:270:\"MEALS: Breakfast only \r\nAfter breakfast check out hotel and drive back to Delhi. It\'s time to say Good Bye to Queen of Hill Station\'s Shimla with life time memories, proceed to Delhi by luxury Volvo Bus [at 08.00 AM] on last day. In Evening arrival at Delhi at 07:00 PM.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:5:{i:1;s:143:\"&lt;p&gt;Evening take the Volvo bus at 08:00 PM from ISBT Delhi or as directed by us and board to Shimla. Overnight journey by Volvo.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:340:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Dinner only &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On arrival check in hotel overnight in hotel. After that come back to Shimla and go for Sightseeing which includes famous Sankat Mochan temple, Vaishno Gufa, Advance study, The Mall Road, Christ church, Scandal point, Ridge Maidan back to hotel, dinner and rest overnight in leisure.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:455:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast and dinner only &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After breakfast proceed for Kufri and Chail sightseeing &quot;Kufri&quot; India\'s One Of The Best Holiday Paradise famous for its Himalayan park, pony and yak ride one can see wide endless Himalayan panorama from kufri, also take a romantic view of Thick Deodar and pine forest, In Chail you can visit world\'s highest Cricket Ground, back to hotel, dinner and rest overnight at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:335:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast and dinner only &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today morning, after breakfast proceed to Sightseeing of Kasauli, there are many attraction places-, Shirdi Sai Mandir, Monkey Temple (Hanuman Temple), beautiful serene and greenery etc after sightseeing proceed back for Shimla. Dinner and overnight stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:306:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast only &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out hotel and drive back to Delhi. It\'s time to say Good Bye to Queen of Hill Station\'s Shimla with life time memories, proceed to Delhi by luxury Volvo Bus [at 08.00 AM] on last day. In Evening arrival at Delhi at 07:00 PM.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:22:\"The Trip Cost Includes\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:306:\"AC Volvo transportation from Delhi –Shimla -Delhi\r\n3 night accommodation for 02 people on double sharing basis\r\nHotel accommodation on MAP basis\r\nComplimentary pick up and drop once during the stay\r\nAll sightseeing by individual cab as per itinerary\r\nAll applicable taxes except Govt. service tax @3.652%\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:422:\"&lt;li&gt;AC Volvo transportation from Delhi –Shimla -Delhi&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3 night accommodation for 02 people on double sharing basis&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hotel accommodation on MAP basis&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Complimentary pick up and drop once during the stay&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All sightseeing by individual cab as per itinerary&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All applicable taxes except Govt. service tax @3.652%&lt;/li&gt;\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:22:\"The Trip Cost Excludes\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:171:\"Monuments entry fees and camera fees\r\nAny which is not mention in above package cost\r\nAny Guide fees/entrainment fees\r\nAny Air and Train fare\r\nGovt. service tax 4.5% extra\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:268:\"&lt;li&gt;Monuments entry fees and camera fees&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any which is not mention in above package cost&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Guide fees/entrainment fees&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Air and Train fare&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Govt. service tax 4.5% extra&lt;/li&gt;\";}s:3:\"faq\";a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"Frequently asked Questions\";s:9:\"faq_title\";a:8:{i:1;s:40:\"How fit do I need to be to do this trek?\";i:2;s:70:\"How long do we walk every day when doing Annapurna Base Camp trekking?\";i:3;s:50:\"What is the highest altitude reached in this trek?\";i:4;s:54:\"What about battery charging and hot shower facilities?\";i:5;s:49:\"Are there ATMs on the way to Annapurna Base Camp?\";i:6;s:27:\"What about internet access?\";i:7;s:80:\"Is it necessary to hire Guides/trekking agency for Annapurna Base Camp trekking?\";i:8;s:36:\"How much do guides and porters cost?\";}s:11:\"faq_content\";a:8:{i:1;s:265:\"Annapurna Base Camp is a Grade B or a moderately difficult trekking route. So any fit person can do this trek, even if you do not have any previous experience. You should be aware of what to expect and mentally prepare for it. Then, as long as you will to, you can.\";i:2;s:131:\"On average, you walk about 4 to 6 hours per day. One or two days can be as less as 3hrs and one or two days can be as long as 7hrs.\";i:3;s:131:\"The highest altitude reached is 4190m. This is the elevation of Annapurna Base Camp. ABC is the highest we will climb in this trek.\";i:4;s:230:\"Yes, you can charge batteries en route. Charger should be brought. There are hot shower facilities as well. You may have to pay certain amount for both ($1-$2). Negotiate. Also, hot water facility could be free at lower elevation.\";i:5;s:240:\"No. There are no ATMs on this trek route. You will have to draw enough cash in Pokhara or Kathmandu. There are a number of ATMs in these cities. Everything is paid in Nepali rupees. So money should be exchanged before the start of the trek.\";i:6;s:191:\"Yes. Internet can be accessed in most places. Sometimes, there might be some technical problems. Internet in Nepal is not as fast as you are used to and at times you can just lose connection.\";i:7;s:547:\"Not really. It depends on you. If you want, ABC trekking can be done independently. You could hire a guide and a porter by yourself instead of going through an agency or not hire a guide at all. Although, not having a guide can be a little problematic during off season.\r\n\r\nIt really depends on you. Is it your first time in Nepal? How confident are you of being able to find your way around? How pressed on time are you? If you go through an agency, it will be costlier but everything will be planned. You will only have to come, trek and return.\";i:8;s:103:\"For Annapurna region, pay for guides range from $20 to $30 per day and porters take $15 to $25 per day.\";}}s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}}'),
