while Upper Dharamshala (1830 m) with the suburbs of McLeod Ganj and Forsythganj retain a British flavor and colonial lifestyle. There is also a large Tibetan community in exile, who has made this their home, living mostly in McLeod Ganj.\";i:3;s:437:\"MEALS: Breakfast and Dinner only\r\nAfter breakfast check out hotel and depart for Dalhousie on arrival check in hotel after fresh up visit Panjpulla a memorial is built in memory of Sardar Ajit Singh, one of the Indian\'s well-loved freedom fighter and uncle of Sardar Bhagat singh. Panjpulla has a small lake with boating facility and is the nearest picnic spot. At Panjpulla, a waterfall is also there. Dinner and overnight stay at hotel\";i:4;s:394:\"MEALS: Breakfast and Dinner only\r\nAfter Breakfast drive towards Khajjiar. Excursion to Khajjiar 24 kms from Dalhousie surrounded by thick Deodar forest. Enroute cover Kala Top Sanctuary. Drive from Dalhousie to Khajjiar is awesome, Full day at Khajjiar enjoy natural beauty of Khajjiar. Khajjiar is also called Mini Switzerland. Come back to Dalhousie hotel. Dinner and rest overnight at Hotel.\";i:5;s:148:\"MEALS: Breakfast only\r\nAfter breakfast check out from hotel and drive towards Pathankot. Drop at Pathankot Railway station for your further journey.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:5:{i:1;s:299:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On arrival at Pathankot Railway Station you will met or assisted by our representative and drive for Dharamshala, Enroute cover Chamunda Devi Temple &amp; Kangra Temple. On arrival check in to the hotel, Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:1174:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After breakfast sightseeing and excursion to Dharamshala and places nearby. Today cover MecloedGanj, Dalai Lama Residence, Dal Lake, Bhagsu Nath Temple, Waterfall &amp; Markets. Dinner and rest overnight at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dharamshala is a hill-station lying on the spur of the Dhauladhar Mo