om Manali)\";i:5;s:35:\"Manali – Shimla( 265 kms 8-9 hrs)\";i:6;s:35:\"Shimla Kufri and Local Sight seeing\";i:7;s:31:\"Shimla-Delhi(400 kmtrs 8-9 hrs)\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:7:{i:1;s:164:\"Evening catch your Volvo bus boarding point in DELHI at 05:00 PM.From there we will proceed to Kullu &amp; Manali by Luxury Volvo bus.Travel overnight on the board.\";i:2;s:372:\"Arrive Manali in the morning,on arrival pick up by company vehicle and transfer to your respected hotel,check in hotel.After fresh up and breakfast,proceed for Manali Sight seeing which includes famous and oldest Hadimba Devi temple,Natural Vashist Hot water spring [known for medicinal use],Club House,Tibetan Monastery,back to hotel,dinner and rest overnight in leisure.\";i:3;s:522:\"After Breakfast excursion to Rohtang Pass/Snow Point [UP TO SNOW LINE] situated an altitude of 4,111meters (13,400ft)On the highway to Keylong is Rohtang Pass. Here one can sees the majesty of the mountains at its heights and splendor. At the top of the pass air seems to glitter against the snow as you look down over herringboned ridges into the Lahaul Valley,enroute visit Kothi,Gulaba,Rahala Falls,Marhi and,enjoy skiing,paragliding and other adventorous activities.Back to hotel Dinner and rest overnight at leisure..\";i:4;s:271:\"After breakfast proceed to visit Kullu Valley Which includes World famous Kullu Shawl industry and their sales outlet,Mata Vaishano Devi Temple at Kullu,Kasol Valley,Manikaran Shahib,ancient lord Rama &amp; Shiva Temple,back to hotel,dinner and rest overnight at leisure.\";i:5;s:185:\"After breakfast check out hotel from Manali,proceed to Shimla by car/Deluxe Coach,arrive Shimla in the evening,on arrival check in to respected hotel,dinner and rest overnight at hotel.\";i:6;s:469:\"After breakfast proceed for Kufri sight seeing &quot;Kufri&quot; India\'s One Of The Best Holiday Paradise famous for its Himalayan park,pony and yalk ride one can see wide endless Himalayan panorama from kufri,a