(542, 1, '2019-08-06 11:05:46', '2019-08-06 11:05:46', 'The Success story of Global Trip Holidays (www.globaltripholidays.com) commenced in the year 2010 with a vision to establish a company which caters to the demand of customers in tours and travel industry with customer oriented approach. Global Trip Holidays is a leading travel and destination management company certified by various Tourism Authorities of INDIA. Our company is well managed by the workforce of young, passionate and professionally team workers.\r\n\r\nIndia is one of the most idyllic ambiences for a lavish vacation, the land of great wonders and diversities and also one of the most visited country of the world which covers snow clad mountain peaks of mighty Himalayas, verdant hill stations, breathtaking beaches, lovely flowing lakes,gushing waterfalls,enchanting rivers, scenic backwaters, magnificent monuments, cultural heritage, fantastic forts, elegant places, terrific temples, intricate churches,colonial homes,wildlife parks &amp; sanctuary,bird sanctuaries,dense forests,beautiful landscapes etc.which deserves attention.\r\n\r\nOur holiday travel packages encompass everything the traveler needs planning the trip,booking travel tickets,getting a place to stay and guidance till you reaches the home. We arrange all tours both for FIT\'s and GIT\'s as well we have the expertise to handle students and corporate groups.\r\n\r\nWe know that you would come to us if we provide secure value for your money,share the savings with you and add further value to your experience.\r\n\r\nOur service starts with offering necessary guidance to plan the vacation and ends with the end of the great holiday trip.It is our sole objective to make ensure customers are satisfied and confident in our abilities to meet their needs.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2019-08-06 11:05:46', '2019-08-06 11:05:46', '', 0, 'http://3.130.191.195/?page_id=542', 0, 'page', '', 0),
